headline: This Mother’s Day, Give Mom the Only Little Blue Box She Needs with Kraft Mac & Cheese’s 14k Gold Macaroni Necklace
summary: PITTSBURGH & CHICAGO, April 30, 2025--Moms know there are few things more obligatory than receiving a dried pasta and yarn necklace from a young child for Mother’s Day. While the classic gift holds a special memory in mothers’ hearts (and perhaps overflowing art bins) everywhere, this Mother’s Day, Kraft Mac & Cheese is helping families level up.
